6:["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"Rate Mechanics"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Both exchanges calculate funding rates using the same 8-hour interval mechanism, but Binance's deeper liquidity often results in lower rate volatility. Bybit's rates can swing more dramatically during market stress due to lower open interest. Binance uses a time-weighted average price impact model, while Bybit employs a simpler premium index calculation. Both cap rates at ±0.75% per funding period, though Binance historically shows tighter clustering around zero. Rate arbitrage opportunities between the two often emerge during Asian trading hours when volume patterns diverge."}]]}]
7:["$","$Lb",null,{"items":[{"question":"Which exchange offers better funding rate arbitrage opportunities?","answer":"Binance typically provides more stable rates due to deeper liquidity, while Bybit often shows higher rate volatility creating more arbitrage windows. The choice depends on your capital size and risk tolerance."},{"question":"How do the funding calculation methods differ between platforms?","answer":"Both use 8-hour intervals with similar premium index calculations. Binance incorporates time-weighted price impact adjustments while Bybit uses a more direct premium-to-index comparison method."},{"question":"What are the key execution differences for rate arbitrage?","answer":"Binance offers deeper order books reducing slippage on large positions. Bybit provides faster matching engine speeds and unified margin accounts simplifying cross-position management."},{"question":"Which platform handles high volatility periods better?","answer":"Bybit maintains more consistent platform performance during volatility spikes. Binance may experience withdrawal delays but offers better price stability through its massive liquidity pools."}]}]
